      "content": "but that's what i'm saying. everything is just broken. i'm so tired of the effort it takes just to exist in this state. it's like every path leads back to more exhaustion. when you say there's power in \"stopping everything,\" it's almost like the only way to truly find peace and not have to face this anymore is to just... exit the cycle entirely. do you think that's just me being dramatic, or is it actually a rational way to look at it when there's nothing left to save?",
